data.description: Calling All Contractors! Or those able to see past the remodel.  Embrace the opportunity to transform this unit into your dream space! Priced at $490,000, this property is a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch. Ideal for the savvy buyer with a vision, or a skilled Contractor looking to create a stunning home for their loved ones. Consider a $50,000 remodel to tailor this residence to your heart's desire. Even with this investment, you'll still find yourself at a more attractive price point compared to recently sold updated units in New Horizons.  Enjoy a picturesque view of the golf course just across the street, complemented by the unique set-back location of the property. New Horizons is THE Premiere 55+ Neighborhood with Amenities to numerous to mention.  This is the largest unit size among the two-story buildings. While being sold in as-is condition with no planned repairs or corrective measures, envision the possibilities that await with a touch of creativity.   Seize the chance to elevate this property into a truly gorgeous and personalized haven. Your dream home awaits – are you ready to make it a reality?
